fc10fbbedf766ad0049f90dc94ffa2891edbc62","tid":1745194,"uid":13318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"defe3bf065078158510b074c11009e08887059aa","tid":1745194,"uid":206304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"記得同老一輩講<br />\n投票處可能有危險<br />\n唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edd5ba687fc221af648b47d1ef94e882c71067c","tid":1745194,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街 比中共管香港 柒事多到"},{"pid":"52e4107539d813f60f059c272ae257ffe3d17c9a","tid":1745194,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去五個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依五個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRyls4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=07fcbc81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3096f93e2911c2ce99e58ae68583f1984c58fd8b","tid":1745194,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"忍一忍"},{"pid":"1c5409f6e14a2a4798a2c819aa42d81bda1cc768","tid":1745194,"uid":21319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:10:13.000Z","msg":"證明政府好想佢亂"},{"pid":"e74707e8ad451f4f9e0b47be51a595f2f4c403f2","tid":1745194,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88922fd92595a99b061f7fc0a88b54ef2a9dfd1","tid":1745194,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"1124全民都投建制派<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745329</a>"},{"pid":"8d1345d27721c95a40aaa44f9f168407ec1b5f32","tid":1745194,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:14:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b451e682b313a921f6d25c015b95fc1f4e068636","tid":1745194,"uid":161157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:15:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b85998d95b9fa1c89d89a9ed1af0a9b0eb23b230","tid":1745194,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"一定會玩狗招<br />\n搜袋搜身 查身分證<br />\n廢老搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749de552f3c8f9ab5d2c9e57bf55fd811e32245e","tid":1745194,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:18:02.000Z","msg":"錄低佢，贏左就算，輸左就告選舉舞弊<br />\n香港人大把錢打官司"},{"pid":"9eb3f2a7fde4d35fe87eacbab0a608dd0a0ded6e","tid":1745194,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d476ed5ba2159b9555644753b17cbf88032a891","tid":1745194,"uid":442,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"5b609135e9319606429363069952574d3c77f