1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T05:58:55.000Z","msg":"CLS 分明想引起騷亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:01:01.000Z","msg":"佢而家咪就係話<br />\n我就係攞支槍黎造馬<br />\n夠膽就聚人黎阻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"如果排隊排到票站出面<br />\n就拉鳩你啲後生, 話無申請不反<br />\n非法集結"},{"pid":"992fa10a173a190d528c4cf1f0f1169cb71a0c48","tid":1745194,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:44:38.000Z","msg":"最多咪話：阿sir我撐你，所以一定唔會投建制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f2b09255e124dcf32e563a530f84db99d1ad0c","tid":1745194,"uid":155012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"後生就直接拉走，投都唔俾投"}]}